'''Damɛ''' (alo '''Mai''') enye ɣleti atɔ̃lia le ƒea me le [[Gregoria ɣletigbalẽ]]a me. Ŋkeke 31 ye le ɣletia me.

Helatɔwo tsɔ woƒe mawu ''Maia'' ƒe ŋkɔ na ɣleti sia. Romatɔwo bui abe vidzidzi mawu ene eye woyɔnae be Bona Dea. Wonɔ eƒe zã ɖum le ɣletia me.

==Ŋkeke tɔxewo le Damɛ me==
===Mɔkekewo===
*[[Damɛ 1]]: - [[May Day]] alo [[Damɛ Ŋkeke]] alo [[Dɔwɔlawo ƒe ŋkeke]]
* Le dukɔ geɖe me la, [[May Day]] alo [[Damɛ Ŋkeke]] le [[Damɛ 1]] dzi.  Woɖunae abe [[Labor Day]] alo [[Dɔwɔlawo Ŋkeke]]le dukɔ geɖe me.
* Le [[United Kingdom]] la, [[May Day]] nye [[Damɛ 1]], gake woɖuna mɔkekea le Dzoɖagbe gbãtɔ dzi le Damɛ me.  
* "Finland's Day" le [[Finland]] dze Damɛ 12lia dzi.

===Nusiwo menɔna ŋkeke ɖeka dzi o===
