* Le [[Canada]] la, woɖua [[Victoria Ŋkeke]] le [[Dzoɖagbe]] si do ŋgɔ alo dze [[Damɛ 24]] dzi.  Le [[Quebec]] la, woyɔe be ''[[National Patriotes Day]]''.

