==Nu bubuwo==
[[Image:Luscinia megarhynchos Istria 01.jpg|thumb|right|Xe si woyɔna be ''nightingale'' le Eŋlisigbe me.]]
Ɣletia ƒe [[xe]] tɔxe enye esi Eŋlisiawo yɔna be ''nightingale''. [[Seƒoƒo]] tɔxewo enye ''Lily of the Valley'' kple ''Common Hawthorn'' le Elisigbe me. Kpe xɔasi na ɣletia enye ''emerald'' le Eŋlisigbe me.

